nodes.text: A cow was a species of creature that could be milked, similar to a nerf. Kaadu resembled tall two-legged cows. On some occassions when  Chef Strono Tuggs stationed his traveling restaurant at Docking Bay 7 Food and Cargo in Batuu's Black Spire Outpost, he served Batuuan Beef Pot Roast produced by Batuuan cows that grazed Naboo's grasslands.
